snippet.title: LEAP - Official Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
LEAP - Official Announcement Trailer
Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/906930/LEAP/

LEAP is a fast-paced, online multiplayer first-person shooter featuring epic battles with up to 100 players, each armed to the teeth. Fight for either the United Earth Defense Coalition (UEDC) or the rebel Exo-Terrans - whoever pays the most, wins your trigger finger and excessive arsenal.

Follow our Socials:
▶WEBSITE: https://playleap.com 
▶TWITTER: https://twitter.com/PlayLeap
▶ FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/playleapgame
▶ INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/playleapgame/
▶LEAP YOUTUBE: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOj-zXNboklNgufYWvmGLmQ

#LEAP #LEAPgame #blueislestudios
